This was my first Fogo De Chao experience, and it exceeded my expectations!
I've been to other Brazilian steakhouses in the past, but Fogo was fabulous!
Sure, I could've made a meal on the sensational thirty item salad bar on it's own, but I took a breather and then went for the meat.
